---


The CaVa benchmarks are adapted from the following original resources;
please also cite the relevant original source(s) when using the
corresponding adapted dataset:

  - CaVaCC is adapted from the BATTIG/ESSLLI-2008 dataset
    (Baroni & Lenci, 2010).
  - CaVaWS is adapted from WordSim-353
    (Finkelstein et al., 2001), licensed under CC BY 4.0.
  - CaVaWA is adapted from the Google Analogy dataset
    (Mikolov et al., 2013).
  - CaVaICC is an original contribution of this project.
